{"tid":1629172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際文宣] 話你知 屙緊屎個陣 你可以做啲乜??","createTime":"2019-10-06T07:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T07:17:57.000Z","uid":239453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0a356404149165f8fc415d01fa614f42eb2dce52","tid":1629172,"uid":239453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:06:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">兄弟爬山 各自努力</span></span><br />\n落咁大雨見到今日都有咁多人一齊企咗出黎真係好感動 <br />\n最近睇連登見到好多人話輿論冇用 到今時今日國際文宣已經冇必要<br />\n冇錯 自己地方自己救 香港人一定要靠自己堅定嘅信念<br />\n但係如果有外國人嘅支持 就更加係如虎添翼<br />\n美國國會議員就算support我地 都需要人民嘅支持先做到野<br />\n但係呢排twitter reddit 開始有好多外國人鬧<br />\n例如話 The anti-mask law is implemented in many other countries and it&rsquo;s actually an incredibly sensible one.<br />\n<br />\n總結：趁住今日大遊行 香港人更加要團結<br />\n平時出街<span style=\"color: red;\">戴口罩</span><br />\n發夢記得<span style=\"color: red;\">Be water</span><br />\n10點係屋企嘅話都<span style=\"color: red;\">嗌下</span><br />\n<br />\n最重要係<br />\n<br />\n大家得閒去廁所個陣就retweet/like 下<span style=\"color: red;\">Twitter / Reddit</span>啲post<br />\n依家#HKprotests 熱門全部都係藍色post<br />\n香港人都係時候做野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1489023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1489023</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1585004/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1585004/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時至今日場運動已經到咗白熱化階段 連緊急法都出埋 冇人知跟住落黎會發生咩事 但係我懇請各位<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好鬆懈</span><br />\n無論你係當中擔當啲咩角色<br />\n都要KEEP 住團火 要贏<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">香港人，反抗！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jV1Tpaq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjV1Tpaq.jpg&h=387b5c7a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e003f9b43939e7dd26376bfe2b31d6e96f6714f4","tid":1629172,"uid":239453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:06:38.000Z","msg":"香港人要反抗呀！！！"},{"pid":"b4f01902b6a0b1c3d533d6fe4338c59a3caf950e","tid":1629172,"uid":239453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:06:49.000Z","msg":"話俾全世界知！"},{"pid":"a34a124734ec38ec391d1d6726f6609866f838ba","tid":1629172,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:07:11.000Z","msg":"以下計劃，請文宣幫手：<br />\n<br />\n【行動】盡快整理所有警暴片段，同納粹暴行做對比，爭取西方實際行動支持香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請幫手推文支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"52178bafab14cc2bb4c14f7c9059e67ef0a7e175","tid":1629172,"uid":239453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:07:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3b268a94256654be8bd21928b0c834b253735c8","tid":1629172,"uid":239453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:08:07.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"639e5e23663790e26387362383e5e9fe8b4dd99a","tid":1629172,"uid":86337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:08:30.000Z","msg":"都要比條link黎架 痾屎痾好耐咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS 痾住屎覆"},{"pid":"5d15d24517e0d6a338fd30e48b73529b49519fb2","tid":1629172,"uid":311550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:08:59.000Z","msg":"98190979<br />\n64616642"},{"pid":"ca4eed7710243313e245b037549affe7b86ec1b7","tid":1629172,"uid":239453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"639e5e23663790e26387362383e5e9fe8b4dd99a","tid":1629172,"uid":86337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:08:30.000Z","msg":"都要比條link黎架 痾屎痾好耐咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS 痾住屎覆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-1